<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎬 Dramabox API Documentation</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .rotate-90 { transform: rotate(90deg); }
        .chapter-input-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 8px; align-items: center; }
        button:disabled { opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed; }

        pre { outline: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px; margin: 5px; }
        .json-key { color: #9cdcfe; font-weight: bold; }      
        .json-string { color: #ce9178; }     
        .json-number { color: #b5cea8; }     
        .json-boolean { color: #569cd6; }   
        .json-null { color: #569cd6; }     
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-black text-white min-h-screen antialiased font-sans selection:bg-blue-500 selection:text-white">

<nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-gray-800 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-lg">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex h-16 items-center justify-between px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-film text-blue-500 mr-2"></i>Dramabox <span class="text-blue-500">Api</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="relative">
            <button id="langDropdownBtn"
                class="flex h-9 items-center justify-between rounded-md border border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 px-3 py-2 text-sm w-[160px] transition-colors">
                <span id="currentLang">🇮🇩 Indonesia</span>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-xs text-gray-400"></i>
            </button>

            <div id="langMenu"
                class="hidden absolute right-0 mt-2 w-[180px] rounded-md border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900 shadow-xl z-50 overflow-hidden">
                <div id="langOptionsContainer"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
        
<main class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8 flex-wrap gap-4 border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i> Dokumentasi Endpoint
        </h2>

        <div id="baseUrlBox"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono gap-2 text-blue-400">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span id="baseUrlText">Detecting...</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm mb-8 text-gray-400">
        Selamat datang di dokumentasi API Server Dramabox.
        Klik endpoint di bawah untuk melihat detail dan melakukan <b>Live Test</b>.
    </p>

    <div id="endpoint-list" class="space-y-4">

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4 border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-400 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-film"></i> Dramabox Endpoints
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition" onclick="toggleAccordion('list-lang')">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold rounded bg-blue-600/20 text-blue-400 border border-blue-600/30">GET</span>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm">Daftar Bahasa</h3>
                    <code class="font-mono text-gray-500 text-xs hidden sm:block">/api/list-lang</code>
                </div>
                <i id="arrow-list-lang" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-gray-500 text-sm transition-transform duration-200"></i>
            </div>
            
            <div id="content-list-lang" class="hidden border-t border-gray-800 bg-black/20 p-4">
                <button id="btn-list-lang" onclick="testGetEndpoint('list-lang', '/api/list-lang', {})" 
                    class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xs font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play text-[10px]"></i> Uji Endpoint
                </button>
                <div id="result-header-list-lang" class="mt-4 hidden p-3 rounded-t bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-xs"></div>
                <pre id="result-content-list-lang" class="hidden p-3 rounded-b bg-gray-900 border border-t-0 border-gray-700 text-xs max-h-[300px] overflow-y-auto font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-all"></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition" onclick="toggleAccordion('random')">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold rounded bg-blue-600/20 text-blue-400 border border-blue-600/30">GET</span>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm">Random Drama</h3>
                    <code class="font-mono text-gray-500 text-xs hidden sm:block">/api/random</code>
                </div>
                <i id="arrow-random" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-gray-500 text-sm transition-transform duration-200"></i>
            </div>
            
            <div id="content-random" class="hidden border-t border-gray-800 bg-black/20 p-4">
                <p class="mb-3 text-xs text-gray-400">Mengambil drama secara acak dari berbagai sumber (Foryou, Recommended, VIP, dll).</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">count (Jumlah)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="input-random-count" value="1" class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded p-2 text-xs text-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="btn-random" onclick="testGetEndpoint('random', '/api/random', { count: document.getElementById('input-random-count').value })" 
                    class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xs font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play text-[10px]"></i> Uji Endpoint
                </button>
                <div id="result-header-random" class="mt-4 hidden p-3 rounded-t bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-xs"></div>
                <pre id="result-content-random" class="hidden p-3 rounded-b bg-gray-900 border border-t-0 border-gray-700 text-xs max-h-[300px] overflow-y-auto font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-all"></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition" onclick="toggleAccordion('search')">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 overflow-hidden">
                    <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold rounded bg-blue-600/20 text-blue-400 border border-blue-600/30">GET</span>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm">Cari Drama</h3>
                    <code class="font-mono text-gray-500 text-xs hidden sm:block">/api/search</code>
                </div>
                <i id="arrow-search" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-gray-500 text-sm transition-transform duration-200"></i>
            </div>
            
            <div id="content-search" class="hidden border-t border-gray-800 bg-black/20 p-4">
                <p class="mb-3 text-xs text-gray-400">Mencari drama berdasarkan kata kunci.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">keyword</label>
                        <input type="text" id="input-search-keyword" value="ceo" class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded p-2 text-xs text-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <label class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">page</label>
                        <input type="number" id="input-search-page" value="1" class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded p-2 text-xs text-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="btn-search" onclick="testGetEndpoint('search', '/api/search', { keyword: document.getElementById('input-search-keyword').value, page: document.getElementById('input-search-page').value })" 
                    class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xs font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play text-[10px]"></i> Uji Endpoint
                </button>
                <div id="result-header-search" class="mt-4 hidden p-3 rounded-t bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-xs"></div>
                <pre id="result-content-search" class="hidden p-3 rounded-b bg-gray-900 border border-t-0 border-gray-700 text-xs max-h-[300px] overflow-y-auto font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-all"></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-gray-700">
